docs.snippet: BERLIN, March 4.--Signs and portents of the political world point ever more clearly to a fairly considerable reshuffling of the portfolios in the German Cabinet. Erzberger's retirement from the Ministry of Finance is certain no matter what the result...
docs.lead_paragraph: BERLIN, March 4.--Signs and portents of the political world point ever more clearly to a fairly considerable reshuffling of the portfolios in the German Cabinet. Erzberger's retirement from the Ministry of Finance is certain no matter what the result of the great Erzberger-Helffereich libel case may be. (It is almost certain to be against Erzberber.)
